&lt;p&gt;&lt;span&gt;☞  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;http://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzA5ODUxOTA5Mg==&amp;amp;mid=2652554077&amp;amp;idx=2&amp;amp;sn=3ecd63f2205fd59df8c360c97c943ef6&amp;amp;chksm=8b7e3206bc09bb10a36b09547efe0c54f41423b180622c1fdc7f14747ccc8f8fecee3a12e2cd&amp;amp;scene=21#wechat_redirect&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; data-linktype=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;span&gt;深度神经网络中的数学，对你来说会不会太难？&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
